# Installation

Clone repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/FinSight-AI.git
```

Install dependencies

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

Run Ollama

```bash
ollama run llama3.2
```

Run Streamlit

```bash
streamlit run dashboard/main.py
```

